<div class="banner-w3l">
  <div class="banner-text-w3ls">
    <% if @home.present? %>
      <% if @home.content1_header.present? %>
        <h3><%= @home.content1_header %></h3>
      <% else %>
        <h3>What is Devrai</h3>
      <% end %>
      <% if @home.site_header.present? %>
        <h2><%= @home.site_header %></h2>
      <% else %>
        <h2>ShivShikar Devrai</h2>
      <% end %>
      <% if @home.content1_desc.present? %>
        <p><%= @home.content1_desc %></p>
      <% else %>
        <p>Devrai (Marathi) for us is a dense but well managed plantation generally on the outskirts of villages. Devrai is a pretty old concept and references can be found in old literatures. There are many popular and old devrais in India which are maintained by locals of those regions.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <h3>What is Devrai</h3>
      <h2>ShivShikar Devrai</h2>
      <p>Devrai (Marathi) for us is a dense but well managed plantation generally on the outskirts of villages. Devrai is a pretty old concept and references can be found in old literatures. There are many popular and old devrais in India which are maintained by locals of those regions.</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
